snippet.title: Elizabeth Warren On Trump: “It’s Real"

localized.description:
Elizabeth Warren is attacking Donald Trump on social media. Is she positioning herself for a vice presidential nomination? John Iadarola, Jimmy Dore, and Michael Shure, hosts of The Young Turks, break it down. Tell us what you think in the comment section below.

“After a stinging loss in Indiana on Tuesday, Sen. Ted Cruz dropped out of the Republican presidential race, effectively handing the nomination to Donald Trump.

And that made Elizabeth Warren, one of the most progressive members of the Senate, livid.

She unleashed a storm of Tuesday-night tweets on Trump, in which she vowed to "fight her heart out" to make sure Trump never made it to The White House.

"It's real," she wrote. "He is one step away from the White House."

Read more here: http://www.businessinsider.com/elizabeth-warren-trump-tweets-2016-5

Hosts: John Iadarola, Jimmy Dore, Michael Shure
